Class ElasticSinkConnector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.kafka.connect.connector.Connector
      • org.apache.kafka.connect.sink.SinkConnector
        • sink.ElasticSinkConnector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.kafka.connect.components.Versioned

    public class ElasticSinkConnector
extends org.apache.kafka.connect.sink.SinkConnector
    ElasticSinkConnector implements the connector interface to retrieve csv data from Kafka, convert them to JSON format using a mapping file, and stores them in the appropriate index in Elastic.
    Since:
    0.1-SNAPSHOT
    Version:
    0.1-SNAPSHOT
    Author:
    Space Hellas S.A.
